{"sn55.74:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 55.74 ","sn55.74:0.2":"7. Mahapannavagga ","sn55.74:0.3":"Nibbedhikapannasutta ","sn55.74:1.1":"“… Nibbedhikapannataya samvattanti. ","sn55.74:1.2":"Katame cattaro? ","sn55.74:1.3":"Sappurisasamsevo, saddhammassavanam, yonisomanasikaro, dhammanudhammappatipatti—","sn55.74:1.4":"ime kho, bhikkhave, cattaro dhamma bhavita bahulikata nibbedhikapannataya samvattanti”ti. ","sn55.74:1.5":"Terasamam. ","sn55.74:1.6":"Mahapannavaggo sattamo. ","sn55.74:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn55.74:2.1":"Maha puthu vipula gambhiram, ","sn55.74:2.2":"Appamatta bhuri bahullam; ","sn55.74:2.3":"Sigha lahu hasa javana, ","sn55.74:2.4":"Tikkha nibbedhikaya cati. ","sn55.74:2.5":"Sotapattisamyuttam ekadasamam. "}